OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Gas stops remote   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fswitching to prepaid meters
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, British Gas has said it will stop      
OL,6, switching people onto prepayment meters
OL,7, via their smart meters when they       
OL,8, struggle to pay their bills.           
OL,10,FIt comes amid growing calls to stop the
OL,11,Fpractice, which critics say puts       
OL,12,Fvulnerable people at risk.             
OL,14,FCitizens Advice said forcible switching
OL,15,Fshould be banned, adding it had seen a 
OL,16,Fbig rise in clients needing crisis     
OL,17,Fsupport such as emergency grants.      
OL,19,FMinisters are also preparing to write  
OL,20,Fto regulator Ofgem about the issue.    
